        <title>Manifold Absolute Temperature (MAT) Sensor</title>
        <figure id="f2650211004" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figk09/K09042.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px" box="no"/>
            <caption>MAT sensor</caption>
        </figure>
        <para>The MAT sensor, a thermistor sensor, detects intake manifold air temperature.</para>
        <para>The MAT signal is monitored by the ECM for EGR operation.</para>
        <para>The MAT sensor is installed in the left side of the intake manifold toward the front of the engine.</para>
    </svcproc>
